The '''blue-ringed sea crab''', a [[Species/Legends|species]] of crustacean from the [[Ocean/Legends|oceans]] of [[Tinallis]], was the favored food of the large avians known as [[tresher]]s. Since sea crabs reproduced so quickly, they had the potential to choke out the other creatures in the Tinallian seas without predation from the treshers. By the time of the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], pollution had taken a toll on the tresher population. In response, the Tinallian government outlawed the hunting of treshers, in order to stave off the potential ecological disaster of a sea crab population explosion.<ref name="COG">''[[Creatures of the Galaxy]]''</ref>

